{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_01_03",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 01 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――朝倉が視察に来ていたダンスレッスン以降も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Even after the dance lesson Asakura came to observe‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_locker-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9733.333333333332,
          "startTime": 10.533333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "瑠依は相変わらず孤立し、嫌がらせを受け続けていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui continued to be isolated and harassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "（私がスタジオに一番乗りか……）\n（今日は練習着、隠されていないのね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I’m the first one in the studio… )\n(My practice clothes haven’t been hidden today.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "（まだ誰も来ていないから、当然かな）\n（でもおかげで自主練に集中出来る）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Well‚ it’s only natural since no one else is here yet.)\n(But thanks to that‚ I can concentrate on my independent practice.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 21.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 21.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "――1、2、3、4、ターン、ステップ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One‚ two‚ three‚ four‚ turn‚ step…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 28.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……ダメね、まだふらついてしまってる\nもう一回頭から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff… No good‚ I’m still wobbly.\nOne more time from the top…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ほんまストイックやんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re really stoic‚ aren’t ya?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 38.333333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "――っ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2000,
          "startTime": 40.333333333333336
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 39.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ずぅっと踊りっぱなしなんやし\n少し休んだ方がいいんちゃうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been dancing nonstop‚\nso shouldn’t ya take a break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 44.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "…………どちら様ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Who are you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 47.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "あらら～……一応、最近入ってんけどなぁ\n鈴村優いいます。よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my… I joined recently‚ ya know\nI’m Yu Suzumura. Nice to meet ya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 53.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "それは失礼しました\n言われてみれば、確かに見覚えがあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I apologize.\nNow that you mention it‚ I do remember seeing you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスも歌唱も凄く上手でした\nごめんなさい、顔と名前を覚えるのが苦手なので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were really good at both dancing and singing.\nI’m sorry‚ I’m bad at remembering faces and names.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 67.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ～、むしろ天動さんに褒められたら\nうち、嬉しくてどうにかなってしまうわ～……ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No problem~ In fact‚ if I get complimented by Tendo-san‚\nI’d be so happy I wouldn’t know what to do~… giggles",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 76.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "それと、他の練習生に囲まれてるのをよく見ます\n人気者なんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ I often see you surrounded by other trainees.\nYou’re popular‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 82.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "その敬語、やめられへんかなぁ？　歳も近いし\nそれに……うちが人気な訳やないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can ya stop with the formal speech? We’re around the same age.\nAnd… It’s not that I’m popular.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 87.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村久美子って女優、知ってるやろ？\nうちの母親やねん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know the actress‚ Kumiko Suzumura‚ right?\nThat’s my mom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 97.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、ただの興味本位で\n有象無象が集まってきてるだけですわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ it’s just out of curiosity\nthat all sorts of insignificant people gather around me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 102.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "大女優……そうだったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A famous actress… I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 106.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのねって……\nそれだけなん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nIs that all you’re gonna say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 110.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。だって関係ないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Because it doesn’t matter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 113.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "そらまあ確かに、天動さんには\n関係ないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s true that it doesn’t matter to you‚ Tendo-san‚\nbut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "違うの\n私じゃなくて、鈴村さん本人に、よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not what I meant.\nI meant it doesn’t matter to you‚ Suzumura-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 122.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "…………え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 123.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "大女優の娘であろうがなかろうが\n鈴村さんは鈴村さんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Regardless of whether you’re the daughter of a famous actress or not‚\nyou’re still you‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.16666666666667,
